{"meta":{"title":"千幻笙的小窝","subtitle":"Awith的小站","description":"T_T","author":"Awith","url":"https://qian488.github.io","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"404","date":"2024-01-16T14:40:18.000Z","updated":"2024-01-16T14:40:18.922Z","comments":true,"path":"404/index.html","permalink":"https://qian488.github.io/404/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"about","date":"2024-01-16T15:26:14.000Z","updated":"2024-01-16T15:26:14.869Z","comments":true,"path":"about/index.html","permalink":"https://qian488.github.io/about/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"search","date":"2024-01-17T02:48:19.000Z","updated":"2024-01-17T02:48:19.307Z","comments":true,"path":"search/index-1.html","permalink":"https://qian488.github.io/search/index-1.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"search","date":"2024-01-16T14:40:01.000Z","updated":"2024-01-17T02:49:14.350Z","comments":true,"path":"search/index.html","permalink":"https://qian488.github.io/search/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"categories","date":"2024-01-17T02:43:04.000Z","updated":"2024-01-17T02:44:28.014Z","comments":true,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"https://qian488.github.io/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"tags","date":"2024-01-17T02:44:53.000Z","updated":"2024-01-17T02:45:16.897Z","comments":true,"path":"tags/index.html","permalink":"https://qian488.github.io/tags/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"VSC与Vim常用命令","slug":"VSC与Vim常用命令","date":"2024-01-17T02:24:24.000Z","updated":"2024-01-17T09:12:20.782Z","comments":true,"path":"2024/01/17/VSC与Vim常用命令/","permalink":"https://qian488.github.io/2024/01/17/VSC%E4%B8%8EVim%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/","excerpt":"","text":"VSC与Git常用命令VSC终端基础 清除终端 clear 列出当前目录中的文件和文件夹 ls 切换指定目录 cd &lt;目录路径&gt; 返回上一级目录 cd .. 创建新文件夹 mkdir &lt;文件夹名&gt; 创建新文件 touch &lt;文件名&gt; 打开文件 code &lt;文件名&gt; 删除文件 rm &lt;文件名&gt; 删除文件夹 rm -r &lt;文件夹名&gt; 查找文件 find &lt;目录路径&gt; -name &lt;文件名&gt; 查找文件内容 grep &lt;搜索内容&gt; &lt;文件名&gt; Git版本控制 初始化Git仓库 git init 克隆远程仓库到本地 git clone &lt;远程仓库地址&gt; 添加文件到暂存区 git add &lt;文件名&gt; 添加所有修改文件到暂存区 git add . 提交暂存区文件到版本库 git commit -m &quot;提交信息&quot; 查看当前仓库状态 git status 查看文件修改差异 git diff &lt;文件名&gt; 查看提交历史 git log 创建新分支 git branch &lt;分支名&gt; 切换到指定分支 git checkout &lt;分支名&gt; 合并指定分支到当前分支 git merge &lt;分支名&gt; 拉取远程仓库更新 git pull 推送本地提交到远程仓库 git push 查看远程仓库地址 git remote -v 删除分支 git branch -d &lt;分支名&gt; Git介绍Git是一个分布式版本控制系统，用于跟踪文件和代码的变化，并支持多人协同开发。","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"test","slug":"test","permalink":"https://qian488.github.io/tags/test/"}]},{"title":"Testing","slug":"Testing","date":"2024-01-16T13:33:00.000Z","updated":"2024-01-17T04:44:50.071Z","comments":true,"path":"2024/01/16/Testing/","permalink":"https://qian488.github.io/2024/01/16/Testing/","excerpt":"","text":"markdown笔记Test 首先，体验一下~~*Typora*~~试试情况 接下来，试试代码块 12345678910111213#include&lt;iostream&gt;using namespace std;int main()&#123; cout&lt;&lt;&quot;T_T&quot;&lt;&lt;endl; return 0;&#125; 很好，基本操作已经实现 接下来就开始补充自己的知识体系，将脑中的内容输出记录，下个文档再见吧hh","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"test","slug":"test","permalink":"https://qian488.github.io/tags/test/"}]}],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"test","slug":"test","permalink":"https://qian488.github.io/tags/test/"}]}